188
00:19:14,791 --> 00:19:16,625
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tentu saja, dia tak dijamin akan ke sana.</i></font>

189
00:19:23,958 --> 00:19:25,291
<font color="#ffff00">Namun, taruhanku berhasil.</font>

190
00:19:27,166 --> 00:19:28,583
<font color="#ffff00">Aku dapat lokasinya.</font>

191
00:19:40,916 --> 00:19:42,375
<font color="#ffff00">Aku akan pergi ke sana sekarang.</font>

192
00:19:42,875 --> 00:19:44,125
<font color="#ffff00">Tunggu!</font>

193
00:19:47,458 --> 00:19:49,083
<font color="#ffff00">Kau mau mati?</font>

194
00:19:50,291 --> 00:19:53,041
<font color="#ffff00">Berhentilah menanganinya sendiri.</font>

195
00:19:56,291 --> 00:19:57,291
<font color="#ffff00">Benar,</font>

196
00:19:57,750 --> 00:19:59,250
<font color="#ffff00">itu sangat berbahaya.</font>

197
00:20:00,416 --> 00:20:04,250
<font color="#ffff00">Apa kau punya rencana, Pak Kepala?</font>

198
00:20:14,166 --> 00:20:17,333
<font color="#ffff00">Kurasa waktu yang tepat untuk selamatkan
