228
00:21:47,583 --> 00:21:48,583
<font color="#ffff00">Ya?</font>

229
00:21:49,375 --> 00:21:50,750
<font color="#ffff00">Kau ikut denganku.</font>

230
00:21:51,041 --> 00:21:52,708
<font color="#ffff00">Ayo buat SIT bekerja sama.</font>

231
00:21:53,916 --> 00:21:54,916
