239
00:23:04,375 --> 00:23:05,541
<font color="#ffff00">Aku punya rencana.</font>

240
00:23:07,750 --> 00:23:08,750
<font color="#ffff00">Untuk membunuh seseorang</font>

241
00:23:09,291 --> 00:23:10,708
<font color="#ffff00">dalam situasi terburuk?</font>

242
00:23:15,250 --> 00:23:16,250
<font color="#ffff00">Aku...</font>

243
00:23:22,875 --> 00:23:23,875
<font color="#ffff00">Maaf, permisi.</font>

244
00:23:27,125 --> 00:23:28,166
<font color="#ffff00">Halo?</font>

245
00:23:29,166 --> 00:23:31,166
<font color="#ffff00">Entah bagaimana, aku berhasil selamat.</font>

246
00:23:33,416 --> 00:23:34,916
<font color="#ffff00">Kau sudah banyak membantu.</font>

247
00:23:35,833 --> 00:23:37,473
<font color="#ffff00">Entah bagaimana aku bisa berterima kasih.</font>

248
00:23:38,375 --> 00:23:39,375
<font color="#ffff00">Aku juga penasaran.</font>

249
00:23:40,375 --> 00:23:41,541
<font color="#ffff00">Semuanya demi artikel.</font>

250
00:23:42,416 --> 00:23:43,625
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak perlu sungkan.</font>

251
00:23:45,125 --> 00:23:46,125
<font color="#ffff00">Baiklah, kalau begitu.</font>

252
00:23:47,166 --> 00:23:48,166
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Namun...</i></font>

253
00:23:49,250 --> 00:23:51,833
<font color="#ffff00">aku tak akan membahayakan nyawaku...</font>

254
00:23:53,375 --> 00:23:54,416
<font color="#ffff00">hanya karena ingin tahu.</font>

255
00:23:55,791 --> 00:23:58,000
<font color="#ffff00">Aku sangat ingin menyelamatkan
anak-anak itu.</font>

256
00:24:00,958 --> 00:24:01,958
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mari bicara lagi</i></font>

257
00:24:02,291 --> 00:24:04,041
