258
00:24:04,833 --> 00:24:06,708
<font color="#ffff00">Baik. Sampai nanti.</font>

259
00:24:37,291 --> 00:24:38,291
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan khawatir.</font>

260
00:24:39,791 --> 00:24:40,958
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tidak apa-apa.</font>

261
00:25:19,291 --> 00:25:21,208
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang harus kita lakukan?</font>

262
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,625
<font color="#ffff00">Siapa pun, tolong kami.</font>

263
00:25:37,708 --> 00:25:42,541
<font color="#ffff00">PERATURAN KHUSUS BERLAKU</font>

264
00:25:42,625 --> 00:25:43,625
<font color="#ffff00">Bu Sendo.</font>

265
00:25:47,208 --> 00:25:48,500
<font color="#ffff00">Aku Detektif Yamashita.</font>

266
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:51,708
<font color="#ffff00">Aku akan membawamu
