267
00:25:53,791 --> 00:25:54,791
<font color="#ffff00">Silakan naik.</font>

268
00:25:58,541 --> 00:25:59,541
<font color="#ffff00">Astaga.</font>

269
00:26:09,791 --> 00:26:11,333
<font color="#ffff00">Sedang apa kau?</font>

270
00:26:12,791 --> 00:26:15,708
<font color="#ffff00">Sepertinya aku kehilangan
