276
00:26:29,291 --> 00:26:31,916
<font color="#ffff00">- Kota Kibi, Kataoka...
- Kota Kibi...</font>

277
00:26:32,583 --> 00:26:33,583
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

278
00:26:34,833 --> 00:26:36,375
<font color="#ffff00">Baiklah. Itu bagus.</font>

279
00:26:37,041 --> 00:26:38,333
<font color="#ffff00">Terima kasih.</font>

280
00:26:40,666 --> 00:26:41,750
<font color="#ffff00">Hei.</font>

281
00:26:43,708 --> 00:26:46,916
