00:26:47,875 --> 00:26:48,875
<font color="#ffff00">Bukti?</font>

283
00:26:49,500 --> 00:26:52,291
<font color="#ffff00">Mari rangkum yang kita tahu sejauh ini.</font>

284
00:26:52,875 --> 00:26:53,875
<font color="#ffff00">Baik.</font>

285
00:27:35,041 --> 00:27:36,041
<font color="#ffff00">Halo?</font>

286
00:27:37,083 --> 00:27:38,375
<font color="#ffff00">Situasi sudah berubah.</font>

287
00:27:39,333 --> 00:27:41,000
<font color="#ffff00">Kini kepolisian prefektur terlibat,</font>

288
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:44,708
<font color="#ffff00">dan kami tahu keberadaan anak-anak itu.</font>

289
00:27:47,416 --> 00:27:49,125
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tidak perlu bersembunyi lagi.</font>

290
00:27:56,666 --> 00:27:57,666
<font color="#ffff00">Kau yakin...</font>

291
00:27:59,166 --> 00:28:00,291
<font color="#ffff00">aku akan aman?</font>

292
00:28:01,708 --> 00:28:04,291
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tak perlu khawatir.
