300
00:28:39,208 --> 00:28:40,208
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak.</font>

301
00:28:43,416 --> 00:28:44,416
<font color="#ffff00">Apakah namanya...</font>

302
00:28:47,416 --> 00:28:49,833
<font color="#ffff00">Ai Goto?</font>

303
00:28:53,625 --> 00:28:56,145
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Wanita yang seharusnya menjadi
