304
00:29:21,125 --> 00:29:22,125
<font color="#ffff00">Ibuku...</font>

305
00:29:25,416 --> 00:29:26,416
<font color="#ffff00">masih hidup.</font>

306
00:29:33,583 --> 00:29:34,583
<font color="#ffff00">Ibuku...</font>

307
00:29:37,125 --> 00:29:38,833
<font color="#ffff00">memberiku nama.</font>

308
00:29:41,125 --> 00:29:42,125
<font color="#ffff00">Mengajariku bicara.</font>

309
00:29:44,750 --> 00:29:47,166
<font color="#ffff00">Dan dia mengajari bahwa aku manusia.</font>

310
00:29:51,375 --> 00:29:52,666
<font color="#ffff00">Dia...</font>

311
00:29:54,708 --> 00:29:56,166
<font color="#ffff00">orang yang paling penting bagiku...</font>

312
00:29:58,791 --> 00:30:00,583
<font color="#ffff00">di dunia ini.</font>

313
00:30:07,958 --> 00:30:09,250
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Namun...</i></font>

314
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:16,541
<font color="#ffff00">aku ingin menyelamatkan diriku
