315
00:30:26,958 --> 00:30:28,000
<font color="#ffff00">Bila ibuku...</font>

316
00:30:30,666 --> 00:30:32,583
<font color="#ffff00">setuju untuk datang bersamaku...</font>

317
00:30:34,416 --> 00:30:35,875
<font color="#ffff00"><i>aku akan pergi.</i></font>

318
00:30:37,416 --> 00:30:38,500
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Akan kukatakan segalanya.</i></font>

319
00:30:42,041 --> 00:30:43,041
<font color="#ffff00">Sisanya...</font>

320
00:30:48,125 --> 00:30:49,708
<font color="#ffff00">kuserahkan padamu...</font>

321
00:30:53,166 --> 00:30:54,166
<font color="#ffff00">Pak Agawa.</font>

322
00:30:57,416 --> 00:30:58,416
<font color="#ffff00">Baik.</font>

