<font color="#ffff00">Mari memercayainya dan menunggu.</font>

330
00:32:12,375 --> 00:32:13,541
<font color="#ffff00">Ada apa?</font>

331
00:32:14,041 --> 00:32:15,958
<font color="#ffff00">Sedikit lagi selesai, jadi, duduklah.</font>

332
00:32:22,666 --> 00:32:23,666
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu.</font>

333
00:32:28,375 --> 00:32:30,333
<font color="#ffff00">Aku sudah lama
