<font color="#ffff00">Ada apa?</font>

336
00:32:38,166 --> 00:32:39,166
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu...</font>

337
00:32:44,958 --> 00:32:46,458
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu sudah membesarkanku</font>

338
00:32:47,000 --> 00:32:48,375
<font color="#ffff00">hingga aku dewasa.</font>

339
00:32:50,958 --> 00:32:52,958
<font color="#ffff00">Meskipun aku bukan anak Ibu
