340
00:32:56,250 --> 00:32:58,000
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa tiba-tiba membahas itu?</font>

341
00:33:00,208 --> 00:33:01,416
<font color="#ffff00">Kita harus bicara...</font>

342
00:33:02,833 --> 00:33:03,833
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu.</font>

343
00:33:06,541 --> 00:33:07,581
<font color="#ffff00">Atau haruskah kukatakan...</font>

344
00:33:10,208 --> 00:33:11,291
<font color="#ffff00">Bu Ai Goto.</font>

345
00:33:17,375 --> 00:33:19,375
<font color="#ffff00">Wah, kelihatannya lezat sekali.</font>

346
00:33:28,916 --> 00:33:30,666
<font color="#ffff00">Perhatikan langkahmu.</font>

347
00:33:31,416 --> 00:33:32,416
<font color="#ffff00">Baik.</font>

348
00:33:35,791 --> 00:33:38,291
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan terlihat sekesal itu, Keisuke.</font>

349
00:33:41,916 --> 00:33:43,750
<font color="#ffff00">Kini kau kepala keluarga.</font>

350
00:33:51,541 --> 00:33:53,416
<font color="#ffff00">Saat kau punya anak suatu hari nanti,</font>

351
