<font color="#ffff00">seperti ini,</font>

354
00:33:59,875 --> 00:34:01,041
<font color="#ffff00">semuanya akan berlanjut...</font>

355
00:34:02,375 --> 00:34:03,875
<font color="#ffff00">untuk waktu lama...</font>

356
00:34:06,708 --> 00:34:08,125
<font color="#ffff00">benar?</font>

357
00:34:10,500 --> 00:34:11,916
<font color="#ffff00">Baik festival maupun Keluarga Goto.</font>

358
00:34:14,041 --> 00:34:16,208
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin itu tak semudah yang kau pikir.</font>

359
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:19,000
<font color="#ffff00">Maksudmu polisi itu?</font>

360
00:34:20,666 --> 00:34:21,833
<font color="#ffff00">Dia tak akan mengganggu lagi.</font>

361
00:34:24,208 --> 00:34:26,041
<font color="#ffff00">Kepolisian pun tak ingin ada masalah lagi.</font>

362
00:34:27,250 --> 00:34:29,333
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka akan menganggapnya gila.</font>

363
00:34:31,833 --> 00:34:33,000
<font color="#ffff00">Seperti biasanya, bukan?</font>

364
00:34:33,291 --> 00:34:35,250
<font color="#ffff00">Minumlah di sebelah sana.</font>

365
00:34:35,750 --> 00:34:37,666
<font color="#ffff00">Kau begitu santai
