373
00:35:37,791 --> 00:35:40,166
<font color="#ffff00">Seperti anak ternak
yang kabur dari desa itu.</font>

374
00:35:47,083 --> 00:35:48,333
<font color="#ffff00">Atau mungkin ibumu.</font>

375
00:35:54,666 --> 00:35:56,750
<font color="#ffff00">Yosuke juga anaknya.</font>

376
00:36:02,666 --> 00:36:03,708
<font color="#ffff00">Apa, Iwao?</font>

377
00:36:05,750 --> 00:36:07,250
<font color="#ffff00">Kau juga mencurigaiku?</font>

378
00:36:08,791 --> 00:36:10,125
<font color="#ffff00">Hentikan.</font>

379
00:36:10,208 --> 00:36:11,708
<font color="#ffff00">Hentikan!</font>

380
00:36:11,791 --> 00:36:14,541
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada gunanya kalian berdua bertengkar.</font>

381
00:36:15,833 --> 00:36:17,875
<font color="#ffff00">Lagi pula tidak mungkin dia terlibat.</font>

382
00:36:19,166 --> 00:36:20,250
<font color="#ffff00">Bukan begitu, Keisuke?</font>

383
00:36:24,916 --> 00:36:25,916
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

384
00:36:55,708 --> 00:36:56,916
<font color="#ffff00">Bicara apa kau?</font>

385
00:36:58,875 --> 00:36:59,875
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu...</font>

386
00:37:01,708 --> 00:37:02,875
<font color="#ffff00">Nama itu...</font>

387
00:37:06,250 --> 00:37:07,250
<font color="#ffff00">Kumohon.</font>

388
00:37:07,875 --> 00:37:09,583
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan pernah menyebutnya lagi.</font>

389
00:37:23,958 --> 00:37:25,625
<font color="#ffff00">Aku ingin Ibu memberitahuku semuanya.</font>

390
00:37:26,125 --> 00:37:27,666
<font color="#ffff00">Tentang masa lalu Ibu sebagai Ai Goto.</font>

391
00:37:32,125 --> 00:37:33,125
<font color="#ffff00">Ada polisi...</font>

392
00:37:35,041 --> 00:37:36,291
<font color="#ffff00">yang kupercayai.</font>

393
00:37:37,583 --> 00:37:38,625
<font color="#ffff00">Kalau kita menemuinya,</font>

394
00:37:38,958 --> 00:37:40,333
<font color="#ffff00">- kita berdua bisa...
- Polisi?</font>

395
00:37:41,541 --> 00:37:43,541
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan berbuat bodoh.</font>

396
00:37:44,541 --> 00:37:46,166
<font color="#ffff00">Kalau kita bicara padanya,</font>

397
00:37:46,250 --> 00:37:47,930
<font color="#ffff00">kita mungkin bisa selamatkan
anak-anak itu.</font>

398
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:49,625
<font color="#ffff00">Anak-anak sepertiku.</font>

399
00:37:52,708 --> 00:37:53,708
<font color="#ffff00">Kumohon.</font>

400
00:37:58,333 --> 00:37:59,333
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu...</font>

401
00:38:00,875 --> 00:38:02,625
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu menyelamatkanku.</font>

402
00:38:13,250 --> 00:38:15,250
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tidak tahu apa pun.</font>

403
00:38:20,125 --> 00:38:21,166
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tidak tahu...</font>

404
00:38:23,250 --> 00:38:24,791
<font color="#ffff00">orang seperti apa aku.</font>

405
00:38:39,458 --> 00:38:40,458
<font color="#ffff00">Ibu melindungi mereka?</font>

406
00:38:44,750 --> 00:38:45,916
<font color="#ffff00">Anak kandung Ibu...</font>

407
00:38:49,750 --> 00:38:51,166
<font color="#ffff00">yang ada di Keluarga Goto?</font>

408
00:38:54,250 --> 00:38:55,250
<font color="#ffff00">Melindungi mereka?</font>

409
00:38:58,833 --> 00:39:00,083
<font color="#ffff00">Justru sebaliknya.</font>

410
00:39:01,708 --> 00:39:03,083
<font color="#ffff00">Merekalah yang melindungiku...</font>

411
00:39:05,833 --> 00:39:08,083
<font color="#ffff00">selama ini, bahkan hingga saat ini.</font>

412
00:39:14,625 --> 00:39:15,625
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ai.</i></font>

413
00:39:20,041 --> 00:39:21,875
<font color="#ffff00">Festival sebentar lagi.</font>

414
00:39:24,041 --> 00:39:25,541
<font color="#ffff00">Begitu itu selesai...</font>

415
00:39:27,125 --> 00:39:29,708
<font color="#ffff00">menjauhlah dari Keisuke dan Yosuke.</font>

416
00:39:31,916 --> 00:39:32,916
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

417
00:39:34,583 --> 00:39:36,250
<font color="#ffff00">Tugasmu sudah selesai.</font>

418
00:39:38,583 --> 00:39:40,291
<font color="#ffff00">Selanjutnya aku yang akan menjaga mereka.</font>

419
00:39:42,666 --> 00:39:43,666
<font color="#ffff00">Mengerti?</font>

420
00:39:47,416 --> 00:39:49,333
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak menduga ini.</font>

421
00:39:52,208 --> 00:39:54,333
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka bilang lebih suka seperti itu.</font>

422
00:39:55,708 --> 00:39:56,791
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

423
00:39:58,166 --> 00:40:00,541
<font color="#ffff00">Izinkan aku bicara pada mereka.</font>

424
00:40:05,625 --> 00:40:07,291
<font color="#ffff00">Kau mempertanyakanku?</font>

425
00:40:12,625 --> 00:40:13,625
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak.</font>

426
00:40:20,083 --> 00:40:22,000
<font color="#ffff00">Lantas, bagaimana aku bisa hidup?</font>

427
00:40:24,916 --> 00:40:27,208
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tidak tahu cara hidup lain.</font>

428
00:40:27,583 --> 00:40:28,583
<font color="#ffff00">Jadi...</font>

429
00:40:29,583 --> 00:40:31,000
<font color="#ffff00">tolong beri tahu aku.</font>

430
00:40:33,375 --> 00:40:34,458
<font color="#ffff00">Kalau begitu...</font>

431
00:40:38,291 --> 00:40:39,541
<font color="#ffff00">kenapa tidak mati saja?</font>

432
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,000
<font color="#ffff00">Keisuke.</font>

433
00:41:11,916 --> 00:41:12,916
<font color="#ffff00">Selamat datang.</font>

434
00:41:14,708 --> 00:41:16,428
<font color="#ffff00">Berhentilah memaksakan diri
untuk tersenyum.</font>

435
00:41:17,416 --> 00:41:18,583
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak tahan melihatnya.</font>

436
00:41:19,958 --> 00:41:21,041
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

437
00:41:21,875 --> 00:41:23,375
<font color="#ffff00">Aku kasihan padamu.</font>

438
00:41:25,916 --> 00:41:27,916
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tidak tahu apa-apa!</font>

439
00:41:49,541 --> 00:41:51,541
<font color="#ffff00">Ini serasa kali pertama kita bicara, Ibu.</font>

440
00:44:04,333 --> 00:44:05,500
<font color="#ffff00">Maafkan aku.</font>

441
00:44:14,041 --> 00:44:15,041
<font color="#ffff00">Hentikan!</font>

442
00:44:27,500 --> 00:44:28,500
<font color="#ffff00">Ambilkan air!</font>

443
00:44:33,916 --> 00:44:35,000
<font color="#ffff00">Cepat!</font>

444
00:44:35,500 --> 00:44:37,500
<font color="#ffff00">Ambil air, sekarang juga!</font>

445
00:44:39,708 --> 00:44:41,125
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang sudah kau lakukan?</font>

446
00:44:42,666 --> 00:44:43,750
<font color="#ffff00">Kejar dia!</font>

447
00:44:43,833 --> 00:44:44,833
<font color="#ffff00">Hentikan dia!</font>

448
00:45:50,666 --> 00:45:52,916
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tahu konsekuensi
dari perbuatanmu, bukan?</font>

449
00:45:55,791 --> 00:46:00,125
<font color="#ffff00">Ini kali pertama
aku melihatmu begitu panik.</font>

450
00:46:02,791 --> 00:46:04,041
<font color="#ffff00">Itu sudah cukup bagiku.</font>

451
00:46:07,166 --> 00:46:09,000
<font color="#ffff00">Nyawaku milikmu.</font>

452
00:46:09,916 --> 00:46:11,416
<font color="#ffff00">Lakukan yang kau mau.</font>

453
00:46:13,583 --> 00:46:14,583
<font color="#ffff00">Kalau begitu,</font>

454
00:46:15,041 --> 00:46:16,375
<font color="#ffff00">akan kubunuh kau sekarang juga.</font>

455
00:46:31,791 --> 00:46:33,041
<font color="#ffff00">Kau juga...</font>

456
00:46:35,333 --> 00:46:37,958
<font color="#ffff00">pasti orang yang menyedihkan.</font>

457
00:46:45,666 --> 00:46:47,000
<font color="#ffff00">Tunggu, Nenek.</font>

458
00:46:48,041 --> 00:46:49,625
<font color="#ffff00">Kalau Nenek hendak membunuh Ibu...</font>

459
00:46:51,583 --> 00:46:53,000
<font color="#ffff00">aku juga akan mati.</font>

460
00:46:55,208 --> 00:46:56,958
<font color="#ffff00">Lepaskan dia.</font>

461
00:47:00,125 --> 00:47:01,250
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana bila wanita ini...</font>

462
00:47:02,250 --> 00:47:04,208
<font color="#ffff00">memberi tahu seseorang tentang kita?</font>

463
00:47:05,750 --> 00:47:07,000
<font color="#ffff00">Bila itu terjadi,</font>

464
00:47:07,750 --> 00:47:09,166
<font color="#ffff00">aku akan menggantikannya mati.</font>

465
00:47:11,791 --> 00:47:13,958
<font color="#ffff00">Aku akan bunuh diri</font>

466
00:47:14,041 --> 00:47:15,458
<font color="#ffff00">kalau dia tak bisa menjaga rahasia.</font>

467
00:47:16,458 --> 00:47:18,541
<font color="#ffff00">Dan aku akan bunuh diri</font>

468
00:47:18,958 --> 00:47:20,238
<font color="#ffff00">kalau Nenek tidak melepaskannya.</font>

469
00:47:21,416 --> 00:47:22,666
<font color="#ffff00">Itu kesepakatannya.</font>

470
00:47:27,833 --> 00:47:29,083
<font color="#ffff00">Keisuke...</font>

471
00:47:31,416 --> 00:47:33,250
<font color="#ffff00">kau akan melindunginya dengan nyawamu?</font>

472
00:47:34,583 --> 00:47:35,958
<font color="#ffff00">Nenek tidak perlu khawatir.</font>

473
00:47:37,875 --> 00:47:40,666
<font color="#ffff00">Aku percaya pada Ibu.</font>

474
00:47:59,833 --> 00:48:00,833
<font color="#ffff00">Baiklah.</font>

475
00:48:03,291 --> 00:48:04,416
<font color="#ffff00">Namun,</font>

476
00:48:05,250 --> 00:48:06,333
<font color="#ffff00">kali berikutnya...</font>

477
00:48:07,708 --> 00:48:08,708
<font color="#ffff00">kau menentangku...</font>

478
00:48:10,333 --> 00:48:11,666
<font color="#ffff00">akan Nenek bunuh dia.</font>

479
00:48:16,458 --> 00:48:17,875
<font color="#ffff00">Kau mengerti, Keisuke?</font>

480
00:48:54,416 --> 00:48:55,583
<font color="#ffff00">Semuanya akan baik-baik saja.</font>

481
00:48:57,625 --> 00:48:58,708
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan khawatir.</font>

482
00:50:01,500 --> 00:50:04,333
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Panggilan Anda tidak terjawab
karena nomor yang Anda tuju</i></font>

483
00:50:04,416 --> 00:50:06,291
<font color="#ffff00"><i>berada di luar area.</i></font>

484
00:50:18,333 --> 00:50:22,000
<font color="#ffff00">Kita mungkin harus membatalkan misi besok,</font>

485
00:50:22,625 --> 00:50:23,625
<font color="#ffff00">Agawa.</font>

486
00:50:35,333 --> 00:50:38,083
<font color="#ffff00">Artinya kita mungkin harus membiarkan
anak-anak itu mati.</font>

487
00:50:51,083 --> 00:50:53,083
<font color="#ffff00">Kau yang melakukannya, 'kan?</font>

488
00:50:53,166 --> 00:50:56,833
<font color="#ffff00">- Sudah kuduga kau orangnya!
- Katakan!</font>

489
00:50:59,666 --> 00:51:03,083
<font color="#ffff00">- Kau orangnya, bukan?
- Kau yang membocorkan tempatnya, 'kan?</font>

490
00:51:03,166 --> 00:51:05,000
<font color="#ffff00">Dasar pengkhianat!</font>

491
00:51:07,666 --> 00:51:10,541
<font color="#ffff00">- Mau ke mana kau?
- Kau tak bisa lari.</font>

492
00:51:11,291 --> 00:51:12,458
<font color="#ffff00">Kembali ke sini!</font>

493
00:51:25,125 --> 00:51:26,208
<font color="#ffff00">Telingaku!</font>

494
00:51:59,583 --> 00:52:00,583
<font color="#ffff00">Apa maumu?</font>

495
00:52:10,083 --> 00:52:11,500
<font color="#ffff00">Lama tak jumpa, Keisuke.</font>

496
00:52:15,916 --> 00:52:18,166
<font color="#ffff00">Dahulu kita sering bermain di sini, bukan?</font>

497
00:52:19,500 --> 00:52:20,791
<font color="#ffff00">Kita pikir</font>

498
00:52:21,750 --> 00:52:23,958
<font color="#ffff00">kunang-kunang akan terlihat indah
di dalam botol susu.</font>

499
00:52:27,333 --> 00:52:29,708
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tidak memanggilku ke sini
untuk bernostalgia, bukan?</font>

500
00:52:43,250 --> 00:52:45,583
<font color="#ffff00">Maukah kau mengakhiri festival denganku?</font>

501
00:52:49,875 --> 00:52:52,666
<font color="#ffff00">Ada dua orang yang memegang
kekuasaan terbesar di Keluarga Goto.</font>

502
00:52:53,875 --> 00:52:56,083
<font color="#ffff00">Gin Goto sudah meninggal</font>

503
00:52:56,875 --> 00:52:59,208
<font color="#ffff00">dan kakekku, sang kepala kuil, sekarat.</font>

504
00:53:01,875 --> 00:53:03,458
<font color="#ffff00">Artinya kita berdualah penerusnya.</font>

505
00:53:07,708 --> 00:53:09,291
<font color="#ffff00">Kalau kita bekerja sama...</font>

506
00:53:14,250 --> 00:53:16,541
<font color="#ffff00">kita bisa membebaskan anak-anak itu.</font>

507
00:53:19,750 --> 00:53:21,916
<font color="#ffff00">Siapa yang membuatmu berpikir begitu?</font>

508
00:53:24,000 --> 00:53:25,000
<font color="#ffff00">Kano?</font>

509
00:53:26,000 --> 00:53:27,125
<font color="#ffff00">Atau polisi itu?</font>

510
00:53:36,333 --> 00:53:37,333
<font color="#ffff00">Sudahlah.</font>

511
00:53:38,458 --> 00:53:40,291
<font color="#ffff00">Aku akan pura-pura tidak mendengarnya.</font>

512
00:53:45,541 --> 00:53:47,458
<font color="#ffff00">Tunggu, Keisuke.</font>

513
00:53:51,500 --> 00:53:53,333
<font color="#ffff00">Aku ingin menyelesaikan ini sekarang.</font>

514
00:54:15,541 --> 00:54:16,541
<font color="#ffff00">Dasar bodoh.</font>

515
00:54:17,666 --> 00:54:19,666
<font color="#ffff00">Kau pikir bisa menakutiku?</font>

516
00:54:22,166 --> 00:54:23,666
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa, Keisuke?</font>

517
00:54:24,833 --> 00:54:27,166
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana kau bisa
terus mengorbankan anak-anak?</font>

518
00:54:30,000 --> 00:54:31,166
<font color="#ffff00">Demi tradisi?</font>

519
00:54:31,500 --> 00:54:32,500
<font color="#ffff00">Demi keluarga?</font>

520
00:54:32,958 --> 00:54:33,958
<font color="#ffff00">Demi darah?</font>

521
00:54:34,625 --> 00:54:35,875
<font color="#ffff00">Keisuke!</font>

522
00:54:38,541 --> 00:54:39,958
<font color="#ffff00">Itu kutukan.</font>

523
00:54:44,125 --> 00:54:46,208
<font color="#ffff00">Aku sudah tahu tanpa kau mengatakannya.</font>

524
00:54:48,541 --> 00:54:50,041
<font color="#ffff00">Namun...</font>

525
00:54:52,875 --> 00:54:54,541
<font color="#ffff00">aku tetap harus melakukannya.</font>

526
00:55:15,708 --> 00:55:16,708
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Halo.</i></font>

527
00:55:17,958 --> 00:55:18,958
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ada apa?</i></font>

528
00:55:21,958 --> 00:55:22,958
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada apa-apa.</font>

529
00:55:25,291 --> 00:55:26,375
<font color="#ffff00">Tak ada?</font>

530
00:55:27,916 --> 00:55:30,416
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa, kau rindu rumah?</font>

531
00:55:32,625 --> 00:55:34,065
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tidak. Bukan itu alasanku menelepon.</i></font>

532
00:55:35,333 --> 00:55:36,333
<font color="#ffff00">Baiklah.</font>

533
00:55:43,125 --> 00:55:44,125
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana kabar Mashiro?</font>

534
00:55:44,916 --> 00:55:45,916
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mashiro...</i></font>

535
00:55:52,375 --> 00:55:55,125
<font color="#ffff00">- Dia bermain kartu dengan Pak Yamabushi.
- Aku kalah.</font>

536
00:55:57,500 --> 00:55:58,500
<font color="#ffff00">Begitu rupanya.</font>

537
00:56:06,791 --> 00:56:09,291
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana penyelidikannya?</font>

538
00:56:13,541 --> 00:56:14,541
<font color="#ffff00">Itu...</font>

539
00:56:16,083 --> 00:56:17,083
<font color="#ffff00">Baik-baik saja.</font>

540
00:56:20,916 --> 00:56:22,916
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak berjalan lancar, ya?</font>

541
00:56:26,416 --> 00:56:27,416
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

542
00:56:32,916 --> 00:56:33,916
<font color="#ffff00">Hei, Yuki.</font>

543
00:56:35,125 --> 00:56:36,125
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

544
00:56:42,291 --> 00:56:43,916
<font color="#ffff00">Aku merasa...</font>

545
00:56:46,500 --> 00:56:49,500
<font color="#ffff00">seperti ada amarah yang tak terkendali
dalam diriku.</font>

546
00:56:54,333 --> 00:56:56,083
<font color="#ffff00">Saat memikirkan anak-anak yang dikurung...</font>

547
00:56:58,041 --> 00:56:59,208
<font color="#ffff00">atau orang tua mereka...</font>

548
00:57:04,916 --> 00:57:06,833
<font color="#ffff00">seperti Kanako...</font>

549
00:57:08,791 --> 00:57:10,208
<font color="#ffff00">aku tak bisa mengontrol diri.</font>

550
00:57:14,833 --> 00:57:15,833
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Aku merasa...</i></font>

551
00:57:18,500 --> 00:57:19,916
<font color="#ffff00"><i>seperti bisa melukai seseorang...</i></font>

552
00:57:22,000 --> 00:57:24,958
<font color="#ffff00">- seperti dahulu...
<i>- Berhenti mengeluh dan diamlah.</i></font>

553
00:57:25,500 --> 00:57:27,580
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kalau sudah tahu sejauh itu,
kau akan baik-baik saja.</i></font>

554
00:57:31,500 --> 00:57:32,500
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

555
00:57:37,000 --> 00:57:38,083
<font color="#ffff00">Kau akan baik-baik saja.</font>

556
00:57:41,458 --> 00:57:42,541
<font color="#ffff00">Kau akan kembali pada kami</font>

557
00:57:43,333 --> 00:57:45,833
<font color="#ffff00">setelah menyelesaikan
apa yang harus kau lakukan.</font>

558
00:57:50,708 --> 00:57:51,875
<font color="#ffff00">Percayalah padaku.</font>

559
00:57:57,750 --> 00:57:58,750
<font color="#ffff00">Baiklah.</font>

560
00:58:02,125 --> 00:58:03,166
<font color="#ffff00">Kau benar.</font>

561
00:58:07,125 --> 00:58:08,208
<font color="#ffff00">Ayo rayakan lagi...</font>

562
00:58:09,333 --> 00:58:11,041
<font color="#ffff00">ulang tahun Mashiro saat aku kembali.</font>

563
00:58:12,708 --> 00:58:13,708
<font color="#ffff00">Kita bertiga.</font>

564
00:58:15,166 --> 00:58:16,166
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

565
00:58:18,958 --> 00:58:19,958
<font color="#ffff00">Akan kami tunggu.</font>

566
00:58:21,041 --> 00:58:22,125
<font color="#ffff00">Hati-hati.</font>

